divs: sighting detailsi was on my terrace having a cigarette at about 5:23 am and each night i star gaze. when i seen what i first thought it was a plane a moving light. when i realized that this moving light could not be a plane because it's flight path was east to southwest but zig-zaging (up & down path)...amazing. and no sound at all...it was weird to see this type of movement...and wonderful. thank you (name and e-mail moved to fi box) cms 09\14\11 07:30 cst flg
